Update the project's lockfile.

If the project lockfile (`uv.lock`) does not exist, it will be created. If a
lockfile is present, its contents will be used as preferences for the
resolution.

If there are no changes to the project's dependencies, locking will have no
effect unless the `--upgrade` flag is provided.

